        {
            "title": "蘋果股價暴跌4%,摺疊iPhone延遲及App Store疲軟拖累AAPL",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/or0bNJ5vfthLMWVvoyCwBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5I13Q_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 蘋果(NASDAQ:AAPL)週二暴跌4%,成為道瓊指數中跌幅最大的股票,多個負面消息打壓股價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該股下跌是因為《日經亞洲》週一報導稱,該公司首款摺疊iPhone在工程測試階段遇到挫折,可能延遲量產和出貨時間表。報導援引知情人士稱,工程開發問題可能在最壞情況下將摺疊iPhone的首批出貨推遲數月。《日經》此前曾在1月報導稱,<span><span><span><span>蘋果</span></span></span></span>將專注於在2026年下半年的旗艦發布會上推出首款摺疊iPhone以及兩款配備升級相機和更大顯示屏的非摺疊機型。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1b82b34f-fc40-32df-ae86-ec3eaba288e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">App Store數據也對股價造成壓力。據瑞銀分析師David Vogt稱,Sensor Tower的App Store數據顯示,2026年3月季度報告增長約7%,受美國零增長拖累。在剔除匯率影響的基礎上,App Store在3月季度增長約5%,與12月季度持平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Evercore ISI分析師Amit Daryanani也指出,App Store增長在3月放緩,遊戲業務再度疲軟拖累整體動能,遊戲收入同比下降1%。美國同比下降2%,日本下降3%,兩者均轉為負增長,而中國則增長7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在週二下跌之前,蘋果在此前四個交易日累計上漲5%。4%的跌幅超過納斯達克100指數的跌幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
