        {
            "title": "Barclays分析師認為伊朗停火期限臨近之際波動性「可控」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - Barclays分析師週二表示,即使伊朗戰爭停火期限臨近,股市預期結果仍將可控。川普總統明確表示,再次延長停火的可能性極低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays分析師指出,市場近期「隨著每一則伊朗新聞而波動」,目前的選擇權定價反映出在4月7日美國東部時間晚上8:00期限到來前存在適度的風險溢價。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告指出,標普500指數選擇權定價合理,隱含波動率在期限到來前保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「與上週相比,標普整體隱含波動率已大幅下降,但4月8日遠期波動率在整個曲線中保持最穩固。因此,遠期期限結構中出現了小幅扭曲。不過,這種扭曲仍然溫和,」該報告表示。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f6bd3bf3-4ee5-3b06-987e-ec301b48c395-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays強調,美國國債、黃金和日圓未能對沖近期標普的下跌。這與2022年的模式相符,當時央行行動和地緣政治衝突降低了傳統對沖工具的有效性。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays明確建議,希望從停火期限和即將公布的通膨數據可能帶來的意外中獲益的投資者,應考慮針對QQQ的跨式部位,目標鎖定4月8日和4月10日到期日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師還指出,鑑於近期的持倉和選擇權流向,納斯達克選擇權(Invesco QQQ Trust (NASDAQ:QQQ))對於希望利用市場雙向波動的投資者來說,是更具吸引力的工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/barclays%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%81%9C%E7%81%AB%E6%9C%9F%E9%99%90%E8%87%A8%E8%BF%91%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7-%E5%8F%AF%E6%8E%A7-145540035.html",
